{"tid":1739813,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"覆核緊急法嘅申請人唔該即刻申請禁制令","createTime":"2019-11-19T17:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T13:55:24.000Z","uid":136683,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f3af486dcd54492923a8de9f54e8faa5c884ca","tid":1739813,"uid":136683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:37:17.000Z","msg":"申請禁制令禁止中國官員就判決講任何野<br />\n，雖然香港司法都好多俾中國控制，唔一定批，但堂堂中央官員俾人禁制落哂佢面<br />\n<br />\n以香港司法界啲blue blood圍威喂，最憎俾人話返佢，分分鐘為左撐返自己判決，都有啲機會批。依家有好強理據中國干擾左判決執行，中司法覆核嘅人申請成數再高啲。<br />\n<br />\n理據一<br />\n人大常委會有釋法權，但法庭有最終決定權，發言人或其他人都無釋法權，除左釋法以外任何言論容易令人誤會等同釋法，所以要禁佢地<br />\n理據二<br />\n政府可能上訴，中國出聲造成不公<br />\n理據三<br />\n基本法列明中國機構同官員唔可以干預香港事務，法庭唯一可以就基本法審訊地方，違反基本法呢條應由香港法庭處理，唔係其他地方，即使個中國官員唔係香港，法庭亦要發出呢個立場<br />\n<br />\n如果一個唔覺意批左就好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a781e632d023c2a4031c592f6be6191e3d38bdad","tid":1739813,"uid":338636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>未瞓嘅一齊入嚟睇致勝關鍵！！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[拒絕分化！]古人一早教我地點贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：<br />\n[正能量撚]出去之前，希望你可以睇下呢個po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1734559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1734559</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>全個連登都係負能量，我要你地有正能量啊</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c430f307d45b55c422fb256f1af30c620176a363","tid":1739813,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"無得執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔通叫光頭瘤sir 上北京拉人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2064459d8e7286af47f991a85b26f1b8782ee4","tid":1739813,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"大家唔好忘記白粉報！出賣手足，一定要搞9佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e6f3d333a556e1bd06fce33d340c4d19dda77dad","tid":1739813,"uid":136683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"呢啲表態夠玩，控制法治道德高地落中國面"},{"pid":"1c32341e1e7f5e5129196f272573320b9eb9feb0","tid":1739813,"uid":136683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2b4b6c2879fb591de2607e9fefb4e65dacf69ce","tid":1739813,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T00:59:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"967f50939b028f3b2347dfb29b0267cb83c10949","tid":1739813,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e67e2f90135b4a5af8a5fed87f3e6d01ccfb23a2","tid":1739813,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:01:15.000Z","msg":"香港特別行政區基本法第二十二條<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"78f33187dc31ecc0ffc9e10f75e1ef01760919ec","tid":1739813,"uid":25108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:14:23.000Z","msg":"佢又拎人大有最終解釋權黎打壓你<br />\n同埋唔係香港地區邊有得你禁制令"},{"pid":"3b8bd5039d5739eacdea5e3223e713c8b0f0bc57","tid":1739813,"uid":136683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"推"}]}